data.description: Wonderful Spacious Home With Lot's of Upgrades! Located Within Minutes to I-264, Bases, and "The Beach". 4 Bedrooms and 2 1/2 Baths ...It's Ready to Move "Right IN" If You Likes to COOK....You Will Love This Kitchen!!  Gorgeous Cabinets, Upgraded Counter Tops, Stainless Steel Appliances and More! There's Even a Special Coffee Nook For That Morning "Wake Up!!  The Living Room and Family Room are Perfect Areas for Use as 2 Separate Lounging Areas....Like One for Shows and Another For The "Football Crew"!! There's a Half Bath Down for Quick Use And For Guests. Upstairs You Will Find 4 Good Sized Bedrooms and 2 Baths. The Primary Bedroom Has It's Ensuite Bath. The Oversized Garage is Also a PLUS!! Outside There's a Nice Sized Fenced Yard, Deck, And Shed!
